from typing import List, Union
from accessor import getValue, setValue

male_avatar_url ='https://public-static-files.superannotate.com/documentation/images/Male.png'
female_avatar_url = 'https://public-static-files.superannotate.com/documentation/images/Female.png'

def on_male_avatar_click(path: List[Union[str, int]]):
    setValue(['avatar'], male_avatar_url)
    return

def on_female_avatar_click(path: List[Union[str, int]]):
    setValue(['avatar'], female_avatar_url)
    return
